Multiple Elements with Same Property: 

h1, a, h2, h3
{
font-family:Arial; 
color: blue; 
text-decoration:None; 
}
--------------
All Elements with same property:
Universal Selector: 

*
{
font-family:Arial; 
color: blue; 
text-decoration:None; 
}

-------------
ID Selectors: 

<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 id="first"> Balaji </h1>
<h1 id="second"> Balaji </h1>
<h1 id="third"> Balaji </h1>
<a href="mailto:balaji@gmail.com"> balaji@gmail.com </a>
</p>
</body>
</html>

style.css: 
#first
{
font-family:Arial; 
color: blue; 
text-decoration:None; 
}

#second
{
font-family:Verdana; 
color: red; 
text-decoration:overline; 
}

#third
{
font-family:Verdana; 
color: green; 
text-decoration:underline; 
}
----------------------
Class Selector: 

<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 id="first" class="f"> Balaji </h1>
<h1 id="second" class="f"> Balaji </h1>
<h1 id="third" class="s"> Balaji </h1>
<a href="mailto:balaji@gmail.com"> balaji@gmail.com </a>
</p>
</body>
</html>

style.css: 

.f
{
font-family:Arial; 
color: blue; 
text-decoration:None; 
}

.s
{
font-family:Verdana; 
color: red; 
text-decoration:overline; 
}

----------------
id: Unique, will be given priority over class. 
class: not unique, can be applied for more than one element. 

#f50af5
------------
Tag with Particular class name: 

<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 id="first" class="f"> Balaji </h1>
<h2 id="second" class="f"> Balaji </h2>
<h2 id="third" class="s"> Balaji </h2>
<a href="mailto:balaji@gmail.com"> balaji@gmail.com </a>
</p>
</body>
</html>

style.css: 
h2.f
{
font-family:Verdana; 
color: #f50af5; 
text-decoration:overline; 
}
----------------
Attribute / Property based selectors: 

<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<form>
<label for="un"> Username: 
<input type="text" name="username"> <br>
<label for="pw"> Password: 
<input type="text"name="pass"> <br>
<input type="submit" value="Login">
</form>
</body>
</html>

input[value]
{
color: blue; 
}
--------------------
input[name]
{
color: blue; 
}
----------------

















